## Problem
On 429, backoff multiplies interval by up to 6 (`Math.min(mult, 6)`). Design asked for exponential backoff capped at 60 minutes absolute. Claude at 15×6 = 90 min overshoots; 5 min providers cap at 30 min undershoot the intended 60 min ceiling.

## Location
contents/ui/ProfileController.qml:552-554

## Suggested fix
Cap with `Math.min(interval * mult, 60 * 60000)` (or similar) rather than only capping the multiplier.

## Source
Review ff0a2eec Issue 13 (suggestion)